  <span id="freeText5378502302575272898" style="display:none"><i>Pre-review:</i><br><br>I strongly believe you guys won't want to miss this anime/manga 'retelling' of the Three Kingdoms. LOL<br>(<a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ikki_Tousen">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ikki_To...</a>)<br><br><img src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1447910248i/17067394.jpg" class="gr-hostedUserImg"><br><br>You also won't want to miss this slightly Boy's Love version of 'retelling' either:<br>(<a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/K%C5%8Dtetsu_Sangokushi">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/K%C5%8D...</a>)<br><br><img src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1447910825i/17067456.jpg" class="gr-hostedUserImg"><br><br>I admit I laughed my ass off when I was watching the few anime episodes of this one...<br><br>Looks like there still are some soft power left in Chinese classical literature after all...</span>
