<div id="review_2795407969" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2795407969" />
    <a title="Levie" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/80458805-levie"><img alt="Levie" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1552340353p2/80458805.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2795407969?book_show_action=true">Apr 22, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Levie" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Levie" href="/user/show/80458805-levie">Levie</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/80458805-levie?shelf=history">history</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/80458805-levie?shelf=tip-top">tip-top</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/80458805-levie?shelf=doozy">doozy</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/80458805-levie?shelf=emotionally-taxing">emotionally-taxing</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/80458805-levie?shelf=great-characters">great-characters</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/80458805-levie?shelf=chinese">chinese</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2795407969" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13573418490036576861">This was ten times more epic then I anticipated it to be. Especially since this is about 90% historically accurate. The story spans generations and follows the sons and daughters of those whom you meet initially. <br/><br/>I wouldn&apos;t recommend this to everyone, it&apos;s very long, and some of the translations and names might be difficult for those with no exposure or knowledge of any of the Chinese dialects. I learned this first hand when I pushed these onto my friend&apos;s lap and he kept interchanging character</span>
  <span id="freeText13573418490036576861" style="display:none">This was ten times more epic then I anticipated it to be. Especially since this is about 90% historically accurate. The story spans generations and follows the sons and daughters of those whom you meet initially. <br /><br />I wouldn't recommend this to everyone, it's very long, and some of the translations and names might be difficult for those with no exposure or knowledge of any of the Chinese dialects. I learned this first hand when I pushed these onto my friend's lap and he kept interchanging characters with similarish names such as Liu Bei and Lu Bu. If you know who they are and what they are like you'd understand how ridiculous that is. <br /><br />People often compare this story to the Odessey, but I have to say, this was far more exciting than that. Sorry Homer, no offense. This did take me over a month to finish, due to the processing time I needed between battles and major events and because of the sheer length. 800,000 plus words. DOOZY. <br /><br />It's weird to think about how much-recorded history there is in Asia. And how much of Asian culture westerners have adopted as its own. This was of personal interest to me but it is truly fascinating and I would recommend it to anyone who loves history or has any interest in Chinese culture. It's worth the marathon read that it is. </span>
  <a data-text-id="13573418490036576861" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


