<span id="freeTextContainer8120267946336191641">I didn&apos;t get around to reading this book until after college, though I knew the basic story. One day, I will translate this whole book and give it the literary style it deserves. The current translations are all wretchedly dated, but the characters are incredible: 100&apos;s of them and all well-developed with their own quirks. It really puts the snooze-fest that is War and Peace to shame.</span>
  <span id="freeText8120267946336191641" style="display:none">I didn't get around to reading this book until after college, though I knew the basic story. One day, I will translate this whole book and give it the literary style it deserves. The current translations are all wretchedly dated, but the characters are incredible: 100's of them and all well-developed with their own quirks. It really puts the snooze-fest that is War and Peace to shame.</span>
