<div id="review_2056990197" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2056990197" />
    <a title="❄️BooksofRadiance❄️" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/68538597-booksofradiance"><img alt="❄️BooksofRadiance❄️" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1513125058p2/68538597.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2056990197?book_show_action=true">Jul 11, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="❄️BooksofRadiance❄️" class="user" itemprop="url" name="❄️BooksofRadiance❄️" href="/user/show/68538597-booksofradiance">❄️BooksofRadiance❄️</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/68538597-booksofradiance?shelf=historical">historical</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/68538597-booksofradiance?shelf=classics">classics</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/68538597-booksofradiance?shelf=east-asia">east-asia</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2056990197" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11169759364666392139">Pure perfection. Cao Cao is one of the most intriguing figures I&apos;ve ever read about. I really wanted to hate him but sometimes I couldn&apos;t help but be in awe of him. I loved him, then hated him, then loved him again....it was just a rollercoaster. And its not just him, this book packed a whole lot of historical figures who were just as equally fascinating.</span>
  <span id="freeText11169759364666392139" style="display:none">Pure perfection. Cao Cao is one of the most intriguing figures I've ever read about. I really wanted to hate him but sometimes I couldn't help but be in awe of him. I loved him, then hated him, then loved him again....it was just a rollercoaster. And its not just him, this book packed a whole lot of historical figures who were just as equally fascinating.</span>
  <a data-text-id="11169759364666392139" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


